-weave selos constant chain, hyme of restoration and chant of battle of psalm of warmth<BR>
-I also juggle between drums and lute if im doing chant of battle(i always use lute if i use psalm.)<BR>
 Now heres a few facts about why bards suck at fighting<BR>
-they have low hp and tend to die very fast if a mob agros on them<BR>
-you need to have very good wepons and a very good skill in 1hs(or 1hb or 1hp whatever youare useing) to deal damage(i dealt good damage at lv16 when i had a brazzen brass kilij and a polished grantint towmohalk.)<BR>
-another thing is if you are out of combat and you constantly use selos constant chain while standing next to the mob it will act as a tount which can come in handy in some sitchuasions.<BR>
-if you keep geting stuned in combat it is very unlikly that you will be able to get you songs out<BR>
<BR>
Now you ee the are many reasons why bards arnt good fighters and if you were me i wouldnt fight in melee post 20.<BR>
